citeinfo.title: Mexico County Boundaries with 2000 Census Data

descript.abstract: Mexico County Boundaries with 2000 Census Data is a polygon theme representing county (Municipo) boundaries in Mexico. Attribute information includes 177 demographic variables from the 2000 census.
